  <Title>Patch 7.18 and Window Client Beta</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>Dark Ages will patch to 7.18 on Wednesday, 10/31/07. The client should automatically patch when launching Dark Ages. If you experience problems, you can download the full client in the download section. Players can also patch by downloading the 7.17-7.18 patcher also in the download section.

This patch will fix the color bug for items and weapon animation in the game.
