&lt;b&gt;Display Selector&lt;/b&gt;

The display selector will be available for players to switch the display settings for Dark Ages.  

1.	Go to your Dark Ages folder usually located in: "C:\Program Files\KRU\Dark Ages"
2.	Double-Click on "DA-DisplaySelector.exe" to bring up the "Dark Ages Display Selector"
3.	Select from the following 3 options: Full Screen Mode, Small Window Mode, or Large Window Mode.  Click OK.
4.	Double-Click on "Darkages.exe" to launch with the selected display.
